      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcc-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se codice a zero                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcc-cli    =    zero
                     go to let-arc-dcc-500.
